### 6 Tata Twagochera   

  **1.**   
Tata twagocheire, Intwe twaremeirwe;   
Nay'obotamero, Twasoroire.   
'Nse'ger'omosunte, Eker'otario;   
Kab'Omoremi'oito, Tat'o'bonsi.   
 Tata twagocheire, totoombia   
'Gw'ogosaba gwaito ntw'abareu.

  **2.**   
Totorie Korw'as' ababisa n'obobe;   
Nay'obotimok'as' okogania.   
'Se chitang'utang'u n'obwor'otoremie;   
'Se chinguru chiao otokong'ie.

  **3.**   
Toe 'buya bwao tob'abao bori;   
Tami'amagor'aito korw'ebibe.   
Twasoroire torae goika tobue;   
Tomeny'amo nay'eng'umbu engiya.

### 14 Nyasae Nintare N' Aye   

  **1.**   
Nyasae nintare Naye,   
Bun' Enoku atarete;   
Mbwate okoboko kwane,   
Inkwane n' Aye boronge;   
Nintaror' enchera buya;   
Yeso, ntare amo Naye.

  **2.**   
Tingotara inche bweka,   
Mwaga nomotindi bori;   
Amatemwa abuchire,   
Ababisa nabange bo;   
Kiria emerindo nyancha,   
Omonene! ntare Naye.

  **3.**   
Korambwate okoboko,   
Ense tekombera kende;   
Nintare nde omoremu,   
Goika ng'ik' Omoerio;   
Ndore omochie Zayoni,   
Omotoria, ntare Naye.

### 15 Kwana N'enkoro Yane   

  **1.**   
Kwana nenkoro yane,   
Ontebi' amangana;   
Nyigwe enkoro ime,   
"Tori aye bweka";   
Igor' cnkoro yane,   
Nyigwe riogi riao;   
Erio ngotogie aye,   
Nchenge ime yao.   
 Omonyerere ngora   
N'obwanchani bwao;   
Mbe omobui bori   
otari n'ebibe;   
Kwana nainch' Omonene   
N'Obwanchani bwao;   
Omonyerere ng'ora   
"Tori aye bweka".

  **2.**   
Kwana n'abana bao,   
Enchera enchenu;   
Baichorie Omogoko,   
Barende barabe,   
Baru' Obogim' as'ore   
bonda bwao boche;   
Omonene oito nchuo,   
karansa na intwe.

  **3.**   
Okwane buna kare   
gwakwanete ense;   
Nindigetie nkomanye,   
Erio ntar' as'ore;   
Nyorokia ngosik' aye   
nkobake botambe;   
Mbwatie ayorigetie,   
'Matuko nde moyo.

### 36 Yeso Nagwanchire Aye Noyone   

  **1.**   
Yeso nagwanchire, Aye noyone;   
Natigir' ebibe nchiche as'ore,   
'Moboria one, naye ogontoria;   
Onye nagwanchete, Rirorio mbono.

  **2.**   
Nagwanchire bun'Aye kwanyanchete;   
'Kabogori' ebibe aria kalwari,   
Ngwanch'as'okobek'engata y'amagwa;   
Onye nagwanchete rirorio mbono.

  **3.**   
Ngwanch'as'obogima, n'as'amakweri;   
Naende ngotogie, buna nde moyo,   
Nintebe komberete ang'e gokwa;   
Onye nagwanchete, Rirorio mbono.

  **4.**   
'Bomenyo bw'omogok' otakoera;   
Ngosasime botambe agwo Igoro,   
Nintere n'egutw' ekomekameka;   
Onye nagwanchete, Riririo mbono.

### 46 Nkoro Nere N'Omogoko   

  **1.**   
Nkoro nere n'omogoko;   
Gankomotogi' Omonene   
Ning' orabotogie rende;   
Obwanchani 'obo bw' ogokumia?   
 Obwanchani bw'ogokumia   
Bw'ogokumia bwa Yeso   
Obwanchani, bw'ogokumia   
Bw'ogokumia bwa Yeso.

  **2.**   
Nere okong'a' mogoko;   
Omorembe Oborabu   
'Riogo 'nguru ase enkoro;   
Obwanchani' obobw' ogokumia.

  **3.**   
Onyigwe gankorangeria;   
Onyimokie, 'kero nkogwa   
'S'obogima, nas'ogokwa;   
N'obwanchani 'obo bw' ogokumia.

### 49 Ng'usa Ang'e N'enkoro Yao   

  **1.**   
Ngusa ang'e n'enkoro Yao;   
Ngusa 'Motoria aye omuya;   
Mbeke as'egekuba kiao,   
Onkenge ontimokie as'ore   
Onkenge ontimokie as'ore.

  **2.**   
Ngusa ang'e, tindi na kende;   
Ndaretere Yeso Omogambi;   
Tatig' omoy' one omobe'   
Nsibie bono n'amanyinga ao'   
Nsibie bono n'amanying'a ao.

  **3.**   
Ng'usa ang'e, imbe oyoo;   
Natigir' ebibe n'okomocha;   
'Mogoko bw'ense, n'ogwetogia   
Ing'a Yeso, oria onkwerete,   
Ing'a Yeso, oria onkwerete.

  **4.**   
Ng'usa ang'e kond' omogima;   
Ntenene as' egetare kiane;   
Ase emiaka eria yonsi,   
Ong'use ang'e n'Aye 'Motoria,   
Ong'use ang'e n'Aye 'Motoria.

### 80 Omonene Rigoro Nainyora   

  **1.**   
Monen'one 'S'ogokumia nkoinyora;   
Bint'amabok'ao akorete,   
Ndora ng'enang'eni nyigwa chinkoba;   
Bioroki'ense okobua kwao.   
 Nkoro yan'eterer' Omotoria;   
Monen' Aye Bw'ogokumia!   
Nkoro yan'eterer' Omotoria;   
Monen' Aye Bw'ogokumia.

  **2.**   
Kongoeta chinsana ime ng'ichana;   
Nyigwa chinyoni chikogotogia   
Gankorigereria korw'ebitunwa;   
Ndoche chioga mbeo engiy'egusa.

  **3.**   
Nkoinyora buna kwaruet'Omwan' oo;   
Kamotom'ache gokwa ng'ichana,   
Kabogori'ebib'as' Omosalaba;   
Manying'aitek'eri'agansibia.

  **4.**   
Kristo karache n'eriogi rinene;   
Kong'ira nka ng'ichorw'omogoko,   
Ntung'ame mosasime n'oboitongo;   
Ndari'agwo Nyasae Bw'ogokumia.

### 99 Enkoro Yane Renda   

  **1.**   
'Nkoro yane renda;   
Babis' emeganda,   
B'ebibe babetereria;   
Gokorusia Igoro.

  **2.**   
Renda rwana saba;   
Timotig'esegi,   
Rwan'as'oboyia botambe;   
Saba ogokonywa.

  **3.**   
'Segi teraera;   
Totig' amatimo   
'Segi eye tekoera;   
Goik'onyore egutwa.

### 100 Tindi N'eki Nyegenete   

  **1.**   
Tindi n'eki nyegenete;   
Tatig'amanying' a Yeso,   
Tinkonyara Omonyene;   
'Bibe biane kobisibia.   
 Yes'egetare nteneine,   
S'ande nigo nkorimera,   
S'ande nigo nkorimera.

  **2.**   
Mosunte n'otub' amaiso;   
'Buya bwaye bong'isane,   
Emerindo kerang'ake;   
'Nguru chiaye ching'isane.

  **3.**   
Amanying' Aye n'eira;   
Binkonye as' emechando,   
Onsi ense gekoera;   
'Monen' Ere nang'isane.

  **4.**   
Karache n'ebitureri;   
Tiga ntoke nde ime yaye,   
Nyeboyetie oboronge;   
Ntari nakomocha konde.

### 107 Omonyamwando Naki Ogosundoka?   

  **1.**   
Omonyamwando naki ogosundoka?   
Naki okorara kogwaikire?   
Imoka bweboyi' ebinto bi'esegi;   
Matuko nkoer' ar' ayerera.

  **2.**   
Omonyamwando naki ogotebana?   
Naki ogotiga eng'eria yao   
Eboyie Omotoria ngocha are;   
'Morototer' amare igoro.

  **3.**   
'Bisaku ebinene nkorwana bire;   
Bianyegerigwe na gokw' omoyo   
Tegerera n'eriogi rie chimbunde;   
Omonyamwando tagotebana.

  **4.**   
Tagoteban' as' omong'uso bw' ense!   
Buya bw' ense nigo bogosira   
Butora chingatare chia omobe;   
Omonyamwando onchoka tama.

  **5.**   
China eris' origererie igoro;   
'Bonene bw'Omogambi kagocha;   
Ngokiamoka bore korw' ebitunwa;   
'Banyamwando chenga na gotera.

### 114 'Mokristo Boka   

  **1.**   
'Mokristo boka, 'Monen' ochikire;   
'Gutwa n' enguba, N'omoro koboko   
Umer' omotemi, Kor' omoremu;   
Bun' omoremu, Rora omobisa.   
 'B' omoremu, B' omoremu   
'B' omoremu, Rora omobisa

  **2.**   
Mechando neba, renda otegesie;   
Toirana nyuma, Gokonywa tikoiyo   
Meganda y'omosunte noyebue;   
Bun' omoremu, Rora omobisa.

  **3.**   
Meromo ya Yeso Yerende mono;   
Renda nomokia, Rwana goik'omoerio   
As' arakorae Genda n'oboremu;   
Bun' omoremu, Rora omobisa.

  **4.**   
Nore nomotang'ani tibwoboa;   
Nako' obuya, Akoremi' ogoke   
Bwanchani bun' ensoko as' eroro;   
Bun' omoremu, Rora omobisa.

### 127 'Monen' Obuya Bwao   

  **1.**   
'Monen' obuya, Bwao bw'ogokumia,   
Ogatong'ense, N'ebinto bionsi;   
As'amatuko, Atano na rimo,   
Ogatimok 'Esabat'enchenu;

  **2.**   
Chinyoni chionsi, Chiter' obuy' obo,   
Ebitunwa n'amagoko boigo;   
'Banto bonsi baitaberi' as'eriogi,   
Ogatimok' Esabat' enchenu.

  **3.**   
Ase tore n'omogok' omonene,   
Esabat'ekoret' Ogosanga;   
Abanto twacha, Amo gosasima;   
Ogatimok 'Esabat' Enchenu.

### 148 Oyoraigwe   

  **1.**   
"Oyoraigwe" aake eriogi!   
'Tom' amang'an' amaya ense yonsi;   
Ens' eye yonsi banyore ring'ana;   
"Oyorigetie, nache!"   
 "Oyorigetie, Oyorigetie"   
'Bitunwa n'amagoko rirandigwe   
Ntat' omwanchi okorangeri' omosiru   
"Oyorigetie, nache!"

  **2.**   
"Onde bwensi" ogocha tatebana;   
Bon' egesieri ngiasie tig' asoe   
Yeso ner' Ekeene n'er'enchera;   
"Oyorigetie nache!"

  **3.**   
"'Yorigetie" ache, nero eira;   
"'Yorigetie" 'remererie botambe   
"Oyorigetie" Bogima bwa kare;   
"Oyorigetie, nache!"

### 191 Monen' Omorisia   

  **1.**   
Monen' Omorisia tinkoremerwa;   
Antimoki'as'obonyansi obobese;   
Ondair' ensemo amach' amaya;   
Nigo akong'irania na komboria.

  **2.**   
Ning'et' ase rigoko ri' amakweri;   
Aye nomorendi, tindi n'obwoba;   
Nondisie n'enyimbo buya kegima;   
Tinkoba n'obobe, Kor' amo nainche.

  **3.**   
Nondageri' ekero nden' emechando;   
Ninyore ebisio ebinge mono;   
Nong'ak' amaguta omotwe one;   
Tinkoboria kende biaisanire.

  **4.**   
'Buya n'amabera kwabing'eire;   
Bimbwatie botambe erio nkorore;   
Mbwati' encher' abakoro baetete;   
Goik' ens' engiya, bogambi bwao.

### 200 'Nsa Ngiya Y'ogosaba   

  **1.**   
'Nsa ngiya y'ogosaba,   
'Mioyo koyanchire';   
Twach' ase Yeso   
Omotoria Mosani;   
Togocha n'okwegena,   
Ere natorende;   
Riogo as' omorosu,   
O mbuya kobao.   
 Ensa engiya,   
Nsa y'ogosaba,   
Riogo as'Omorosu,   
O mbuya kobao.

  **2.**   
'Nsa ngiya y'ogosaba,   
'Motoria kar' ang'e;   
As' amabera abaigw'   
abana baye;   
Atotebia tomoe,   
Ogwechanda gwaito;   
Riogo as' omorosu,   
O mbuya kobao.

  **3.**   
'Nsa ngiya y'ogosaba,   
Ker' abatemirwe';   
Bakoretera Yes'   
obororo bwabo;   
N'enkoro y'amabera,   
narusie mochando;   
Riogo as' omorosu,   
O mbuya kobao.

  **4.**   
As' Ensa y'ogosaba,   
Twegenir' as'are;   
Ebisio toganetie natobinyore;   
Ase oboikerenu,   
Tosirie mechando;   
Riogo as' omorosu,   
O mbuya kobao.

### 208 Ens'enyia Y'Omwando   

  **1.**   
Yes'Omonene,   
Er'otoriereir' eira;   
Eira y'obomeny'   
Atoroseirie aria Igoro;   
'Mochie bw'abaya,   
Enka y'omwando twaeirwe;   
As'ebibe n'emechando   
n'amakweri bitabe.   
 Ens'e ----- nyia, y'omwando;   
('Nse y'omwand'ekare gocha) x 2   
Yes'A ----- toroseirie;   
('Mochie Yes'Atoroseirie) x 2   
Tome ----- nye, botambe;   
(Tomeny'aroro botambe) x 2   
Tomenye n'omorembe   
as'ens'eria botakoira.

  **2.**   
As'ens'eyi'enyia,   
Botuko mbokob'aroro;   
Yeso ner'orab'omobaso   
irumbe ritatube;   
'Botaka mboiyo,   
gose kende kiogoichania;   
Tomenye nomorembe,   
N'Omotori'oito botambe

  **3.**   
Ntoumerane n'abasani   
twatiganete;   
Baria bonsi bararet'ase   
Yeso nababeo;   
Ne chintakana   
nchinyor'abaibori babo;   
'Bororo bw'amakweri   
titokoboinyora rinde.

  **4.**   
'Basani baito,   
rigereria bosio rioka;   
Intwe nabaeti,   
bamint'ens'eye teri seito;   
Titweb'eira, Y'ense   
Yes'Atoroseirie;   
Intwe n'abanyamwando   
b'obogima botakoera.

### 283 Otobatise, As' Omoik'Oo   

  **1.**   
Otobatise, As'Omoik'oo;   
As'obwanchani tobeke chinguru.   
 Twagosabire Yes'Omotori'oito;   
'S'Omoika n'obwanchani tobatise.

  **2.**   
Twarer'as'ore, Ntw'abanyabibe;   
Tosibie, tochene korw'as'ebibe.

  **3.**   
Iruma ria Igoro, Ika korwa Igoro;   
Twasab'ebisio, 'S'amabera nchw'ang'e.

  **4.**   
Igwa eriogi, Riarwete lgoro;   
Ay'Omwanchw'one, Ngokiri'as'ore.   
 Natokobake, Eng'ondi yaitetwe;   
Natogosasime, Amen, Amen.

### 322 Yeso n'Omotoria Bw'ogokumia   

  **1.**   
Yeso n'Omotori'are bw'ogokumia;   
Noyo bw'ogokumi'ase nde;   
Abis'enkoro yan'as' egetare;   
'Se chindoche chi'omogoko.   
 'Bisir'enkoro ime y'egetare,   
'S'ekiriri ens'enyomo;   
'Bisir'enkoro 's'obwanchani bwaye,   
Na gontuba n'okoboko,   
Na gontuba n'okoboko.

  **2.**   
Yeso n'Omotori'are bw'ogokumia;   
Nig'agotang'emechando,   
Ambogoria ase amabok'aye;   
Ang'a chinguru botambe.

  **3.**   
Ansesenia nebisi'ebinge mono;   
Ang'ichoria n'obochenu;   
Kanaonchoirwe ninter'omogano;   
Bw'Omoboria on'Omuya.

  **4.**   
Karambisi'Oborabu anyimokie;   
Toumeran'as'amare;   
Ntogie Ogotoreka n'obwanchani;   
N'emeganda y'abachenu.

### 323 Yeso n'Omosani On'are   

  **1.**   
Yeso n'Omosani on'are,   
Nere bionsi ase nde;   
'S'enkoro yane nabuete bonsi;   
Nig'are bun'egesicha kie rigok'ase nde;   
'Kinganetie nsibigwe mb'omogima.   
'S'obor'andemia, 's'emechand'ambisia;   
Antebia motwek' amakong'u onsi.   
 Ner'egesicha ekiya,   
Ng'enang'eni endabu; '   
S'enkoro yane nabuete bonsi.

  **2.**   
Er'ondusiri'ogwechanda,   
N'obororo bwane;   
Nere obotamer' as' amatemwa;   
Natugutire bionsi pi,   
Nony'emebwekano;   
Korw'enkoro ner'or'omorendi, one.   
'Nse yonsi yanyangire,   
Na saitani antema;   
Konde na Yeso nimb' omobui.

  **3.**   
Yaya ere tagontiga,   
Gose Kombwatoka;   
Ko mwegenete na komokorera;   
Ongiteire n'omorero,   
Tinkwoboa kende;   
'Nyigotirie n'endagera ya Igoro.   
Ninso' as' obonene,   
Ndor'obosio bwaye;   
'Se chindoche chiomogoko chire.

### 326 Mbwat' Omorisia   

  **1.**   
Mbwat' Omorisia Oyonyanchete;   
Ansesenia nche Ntanyare kwera;   
'S'Omosalab' agachandek' agakwa;   
Erio meny' as'obwanchani bwaye.   
 Gotunya Yeso kera rituko;   
Kende nkegonsaria kare nainche;   
'Mosunte gose omobaso;   
Yes'omorisi' one nere bionsi.

  **2.**   
'Borisi'obonge aru'ase tore;   
Mache aeta ng'ora ase'nde,   
'Buya n'amabera bintunya nchera;   
Tinkoremerwa kare nainche.

  **3.**   
Kondatayaye nsire enchera;   
Ere nang'use 'ng'iranie nchera,   
Nonya nobokong'u Nche tinkwoboa;   
Morisi'Omuya Nandende rioka.

  **4.**   
Merem' eere Rogendo boigo;   
Ere nandae gochia Bwone nka,   
Agw'ase ndamenye 'Mogoko bori;   
Nabanchwa ase Amagor' Aye.

### 333 Mobake Nyasae    

  **1.**   
Mobake Nyasae, Mogambi ore Igoro;   
Oyore' emiaka yonsi, Omwanchanii;   
'Monene Yehova, Ense na Igoro;   
Twaribak'erieta riao, Ribakwe bo.

  **2.**   
Mobake Nyasae, 's'ogochika kwaye;   
Ndw'as'ense ndigi'Omogoko, As'ar'ere;   
Ntige bionsi ebiense, 'Bonene, chisemi;   
Mokor' ere bweka koba, 'Nguba yane.

  **3.**   
Omoganda bwensi, Mobake Nyasae;   
Tata, Omwana n'Omoika, 'Kero gionsi;   
Motogie Nyasae, Mbwatisi'aba Igoro;   
'Bonene bwensi n'obwao, N'ebako bo.

### 369 Nomwegene Yeso   

  **1.**   
Nomwegene Yeso and' onsi as' ore?;   
Nar' enkoro yao kera rituko?   
Nor' omworokigwa? motemo' orore;   
Nak'Omoika, omonge kegima.   
 'Bogim' obonge, 'bogim' bonge;   
Erio babe n'obogim' obonge   
'Bogim' obonge, 'bogim' obonge;   
Erio nabe n'obogim' obonge.

  **2.**   
'S'obwanchani bwaye, orari'erieta,   
Ri'Omotori'omuya, orwete igoro,   
Bachenu sasima ase Ring'ana;   
Rikorw' ogotorek' as' amanyinga.

  **3.**   
Inchwo mwegenete, 'gw'okorangeria;   
Bionsi korw' as' Are, naye moe bo,   
Yeso nagwanchere Korach'as'Are;   
Naka'ogosesenigw'okonene.
